Geoff!

01:27:10.629 --> 01:27:12.062
Geoff!

01:27:14.785 --> 01:27:16.882
- Geoff!
- Ronald!

01:27:17.782 --> 01:27:19.327
Geoffrey!

01:27:21.085 --> 01:27:23.286
Ronald!

01:27:27.053 --> 01:27:28.744
Geoff!

01:27:32.487 --> 01:27:33.917
O que é isso?

